  "Description": {
    "English": "An automatically-regulated lubricant dispenser fitted to the leg joints of the Minotaur reduce friction and encourage fuel-efficient motion.<br><br>Significantly <span class=\"name name-stellar\">reduces fuel burn</span> in the Minotaur's Daedalus Engine.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "安装在弥诺陶洛斯腿部接合处的自动调节润滑剂分配器，可减少摩擦，并促进节能运动。<br><br>显著减少弥诺陶洛斯搭载的代达罗斯引擎的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">燃料消耗</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有自動調節功能的潤滑劑分注器，能安裝到彌諾陶洛斯腿部關節，減少摩擦，能節省行動消耗的燃料。<br><br>針對彌諾陶洛斯的代達洛斯引擎，大幅<span class=\"name name-stellar\">降低燃料消耗</span>。"
  },
